results.description:
It may be strange to go to The Hague for an EOS Amsterdam meetup, to explain, EOS Amsterdam is the name of the founding block producer initiative.

The place "En Passent" looks like a residential place, the door is open so just walk in. I'm sitting there with fresh coffee, drinks against bar price 1,50, electricity and wifi is free of charge!

https://www.google.nl/maps/@52.0733407,4.3113645,3a,75y,210.85h,88.66t/data=!3m6!1e1!3m4!1sx6kJRPQxm7dSpkteX0xzrw!2e0!7i13312!8i6656

Bring you laptops so we can play around with EOS. To run a local testnet you can follow along this guide for the dawn-2.x version.

https://steemit.com/eos/@monetashi/eos-development-screencast-running-a-single-node-local-testnet-macos

Looking forward to meeting you all!

Regards Boy Maas
results.name: EOS Amsterdam introduction & General Talk

results.description:
It may be strange to go to The Hague for an EOS Amsterdam meetup, to explain, EOS Amsterdam is the name of the founding block producer initiative.

The place "En Passent" looks like a residential place, the door is open so just walk in. I'm sitting there with fresh coffee, drinks against bar price 1,50, electricity and wifi is free of charge!

https://www.google.nl/maps/@52.0733407,4.3113645,3a,75y,210.85h,88.66t/data=!3m6!1e1!3m4!1sx6kJRPQxm7dSpkteX0xzrw!2e0!7i13312!8i6656

Pareto principles work against the stake model, especially when all the little fish are not aware and do not unite. These are very interesting conversations to have, and the governance channel of the EOSGo channel is very busy at the moment as the constitution and details on governance and arbitration touch all vested members ...

https://forums.eosgo.io/categories/eos-governance-economics-philosophy

Draft constitution

https://forums.eosgo.io/discussion/424/design-principles-of-my-v0-1-draft-eos-io-constitution

Looking forward to meeting you all!

Regards Boy Maas

results.description:
EOS main-net launch is a few weeks away, and many dApps are moving to the EOS platform. A lot of trust is placed in the technology. One of the big announcements was Tesloop on EOS. Join us for a discussion, general questions and to meet fellow EOS enthousiasts!

BIG THANKS to "Van Ons" for hosting this meetup!!! <3

Watchlist:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=2261&v=eYdC8ipplmQ
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Fu4tr307NPA
results.name: General discussion & Tesloop on EOS

results.description:
EOS Block Chain platform is rapidly gaining momentum as it solves most of the current block chain challenges with authentication, performance and NO transaction fees. Maybe even more important, EOS will allow everyone, small and enterprise, to build a healthy business case.

EOS Mainnet launches in June and already many dApps are moving or planning to move to the EOS block chain platform. A lot of trust is placed in the technology and a lot of talks are about the constitution. Join us for a discussion, general questions and to meet fellow EOS enthousiasts!
results.name: EOS Launch & Distributed Apps
